					<description><![CDATA[<p><img width="612" height="408" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/image-314.png" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/image-314.png?w=612&amp;ssl=1 612w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/image-314.png?resize=219%2C146&amp;ssl=1 219w" sizes="(max-width: 612px) 100vw, 612px" /></p>
